Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.19,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"August"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:09.87,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"September"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:09.87,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}"Narukain deadline"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:10.90,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Narukain deadline"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just two more weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The more I hurry, the harder it is to write something good...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:23.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming to this island, I sometimes get this urge to write calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:28.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Something rises from inside me, and my hands start to shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get that shake back in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:37.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll feel better if I take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't click...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:53.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not turning on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:54.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:58.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Okega Makucchishita"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Translation: Was almost seriously injured"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:46.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take for someone to come and fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:49.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Maybe about a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Figured as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:54.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... While we're at it, you wanna try it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! A bath boiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can heat the bath by burning firewood in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:08.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! We use the boiler at our house too, and it's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but... But what about the firewood? I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:17.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mountain right there, so it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The branches have to be dry, or else they won't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:28.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... He's already in the groove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell him this is a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:32.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's more over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do this for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Village Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This should be enough branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure hope you find a wife who'll keep the fire for you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:58.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,More than a wife, I want a bath with a gas-powered water heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're twenty-three years old already, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a girlfriend you're thinking of marrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been writing calligraphy all this time, so... How can I word this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the type who would die alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't denying what I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you should be good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:24.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:27.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the smoke there coming from around Sensei's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A bonfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You think Sensei would do that kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it? Sensei, you're such a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:46.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's a bath, then it's okay.\NEven Naru can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:53.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always keepin' watch of the fire when Grandpa is takin' a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,44)}"How's the water, sir?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Good, but put the fire out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,107)}if it gets outta hand"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me. I'm used to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:04.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The prep is a pain, but it is exciting, like taking a dip in a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, was it too hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's so relaxing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:23.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the stress melting away. I can see why the Village Leader is so into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was heated with all that effort, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Why are they here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They came here thinkin' it was a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, having a kid watch the fire while you take a leisurely bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment, we'll take a look at you nude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I bet ya want young gals to look at ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a flasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no fire here, so get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, he doesn't go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the camera for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to take some shots for reference material.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:04.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Reference...? Even in manga, nude's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Just need to censor the tip...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Only a little.\N--I can't relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, how 'bout we try this?\N--Taking a bath in the afternoon isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:18.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? What?\N--For now, I just need to wait for them to get bored, and leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Was it hot, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?! Look at how red I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!\N--Wait, you come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I feel fresh and new again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, time to write...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro! Wh-What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:45.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's not home today, so I'll make lunch for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But why here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, cut the cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:56.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Sugar"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:54.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Add miso and sugar to your liking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then add the cut cucumbers, and mix them together lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:01.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cucumbers with miso are ready with these easy steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that easy, I feel like I can make it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, cut the cucumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Add miso and sugar, then mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ready!\N--Sensei, did you see what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's the same, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the same eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:20.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looking bad yet tasting good is what a man's cooking is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way. That's gotta taste bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... Yours tastes horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:35.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How come I can only taste the cucumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this tastes bad after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! You said it tasted good just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say it tasted good.\NIt only tastes like miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:47.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so stubborn? So immature...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "immature"?!\NSpeaking to an elder like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't point your finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're supposed to be an elder, act like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:05.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Hina?! Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip! Moaning isn't going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush her, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, take a drink and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She came running over here, so it's got to be an emergency. Spill it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so impatient over a kid's emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:19.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's bothersome, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And that's immature, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Just calm down, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please, we'll listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:34.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's being bullied by the big kids from the other village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:47.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, that looks fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina--! Heeelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You brought back some adults?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:00.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you brats come from?\NThis is their playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, bozo fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is our place now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bozo fox...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Must be the brats from Rokunosaki Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a neighbor village we've been feuding with since my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Get them outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were playin' here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You visiting brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you call someone you've never met before "bozo fox"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:29.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How am I a fox? Sure, people say my eyes are unpleasant sometimes, but only sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:32.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's really taking this personal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, ya wimpy bean sprout! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The pain... Why is my heart in pain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That brat's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:46.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He saw through Sensei as a loser and a wimp, even when they just met for the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use using strong words against brats like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, brats!\N--A blondie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's blond...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Ya gonna try to scare us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You kids are older, so can ya let these young ones have the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if ya really mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...kneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Calm down, Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go! I'm gonna show 'em a thing or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:14.88,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"*innowasso = spiteful brat"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya freakin' stupid brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--You'll get into trouble if you seriously hit them...\N--The adults are bein' violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:22.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Sensei... Naru and everyone\N--Yankee, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--wanna play dodgeball here.\N--Get outta here, outsiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, we can't draw back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:32.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are relying on me...\NNow is the time to dignify myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya want, ya limp noodle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Limp... noodle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're adults, so we won't resort to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:47.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But if you kids loiter any longer,\NI'll need to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whazzat? Who're ya plannin' to call?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}police{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are ya pullin' the cops into this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:58.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make an anonymous call that you kids are bullying other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:01.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be embarrassing being taken away, and your parents will be ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your lives will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:06.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! Adult tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... So immature...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! You an' yer dirty tricks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you deal the finishing blow to my mobile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya mean, "finishin' blow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:25.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You only got poop on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you, brat! Look what you've done to my partner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,that I've been using as a watch, even when I couldn't use it as a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:34.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Couldn't use it as a phone"?\NYa tricked us kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Being angry at me when you're the one who humiliated my mobile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro. Were you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, of course I wouldn't laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's that all 'bout?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave 'em be, and play ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:55.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei! They're ignoring us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself! You kids go back to your village's playground...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Our playground's been taken over by middle schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:07.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,By one super strong fightin' girl, and another with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothin' to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yer not gonna beat us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:21.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If'n ya do, we're gonna tell our parents the adults here hit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If ya adults hit kids, then yer really gonna get it from the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're gonna be caught fer child abuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have people saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:35.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, adults should never hit children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru? Those kids are saying that they're going to play baseball here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just let them play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Been telling ya to get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll play some dodgeball...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Ya let us have this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have fun playing baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just play among ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:01.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Sensei are going to be outfield.\NYou guys run around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! This is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:09.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's our Sensei.\NGoing all-out even against kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It don't mean nothin' if it doesn't hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Klutz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He hit it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If they get the ball, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! You're supposed to be adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Supposed to be adults...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we are adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In this hot weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Akki!\N--Akki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doin' over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't clear the game I played the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids! This isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're good already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna play with Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have interrupted your game there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't what it was about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Akki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...really mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... Let's play a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pulling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Tarzan! Let's play Tarzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Tarzan?\N--There's a place right down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what the heck? But only for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! C'mon, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I haven't seen a real Tarzan experience like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--It's easy!\N--It's not easy! That's just an ivy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna show ya how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like... this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...? It doesn't look fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It's your turn next, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:12.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Heck, no!\N--How come? It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lame! You're supposed to be an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:18.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see you say the same once you grow to the size of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:22.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way this can hold the weight of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But if it can support {\i1}all{\i0} of you, then things are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, dang it! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then yer gonna do it, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:36.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, whatever. Just don't do anything dangerous in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! This is gonna be super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:44.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably trying to convey the fun to me, but I'm not feeling it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna get hurt one of these days with this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:51.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for the kids, but I need to get rid of dangerous playthings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fake my jump, and break this off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it!\N--Stop it, Sensei! You're pullin' it too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--It's gonna break!\N--Stop it! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:08.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kids all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was super scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,thought I was gonna die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thought I was gonna die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine... It's just a graze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to use mugwort!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Look for them mugworts!\N--Don't worry. It's not that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Mugwort!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This herb's gonna stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's just going to infect me with germs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This way's the shortcut home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:57.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today was another day wasted in vain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:01.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gaining much from playing with the kids every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:06.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to just wait for the moment when I get the urge to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Time is closing in on me fast... Real fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's here... It's really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The god of calligraphy is upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:28.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it was so easy to find something I want to write about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to hurry back and write!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can write...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's not behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he went back another way by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Sensei's always like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?\N--Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Sensei's not home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one was here when we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei disappeared when we were comin' back from the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he got trapped by the monster in the mountains, and is being munched on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:15.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not that there are any monsters, but I am worried that he's not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:19.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's lost in the mountains, it's not like it's a dense forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit? Stop freaking me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:32.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And just when I felt like I could write a great piece of calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:36.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The time I spent playing with the kids just a while back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,already feels like a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:45.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! Panic is making my brain fabricate memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm... Stay calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to go up a little more, and I'll be back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:56.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Seishu! Do your best, Seishu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch... This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:14.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Help should be here by now.\NWhere is everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:17.92,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Typical earthquake survival pose"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:18.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being stranded in the mountains is the pinnacle of solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, literally going to "die alone"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:27.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help me... Anyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a key...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the key to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:47.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A spare key... I lost it... Maybe it was when I was playing in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is so stupid! Why am I losing my cool in the mountains in my backyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:00.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one gets stranded near their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:06.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:11.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Is this outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:17.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please let my bath be fixed... Please let my bath be fixed... Please let my bath be fixed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go back home so that I can write calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See? I knew he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:29.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder we couldn't find him on the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:33.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... I'm so glad you're safe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it... That took too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sensei crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Great, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Here's the first-aid kit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.45,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Seishu Handa"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:03.01,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Stars"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration is important after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:47.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return.
